{"tid":1854440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[連戰鬥民族都頂唔住] 俄羅斯發現首2宗武漢肺炎確診個案","createTime":"2020-01-31T13:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T14:25:28.000Z","uid":231040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f768b0d86a1644745158afb26b9aa460bf40f969","tid":1854440,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯「淨土」被攻破！　莫斯科證實發現2例武漢肺炎確診<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1635481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1635481&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=7fc20a17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1635481</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯「淨土」淪陷！根據RT報導，俄國副總理戈利科娃（Tatiana Golikova），俄國境內出現2例新型冠狀病毒（武漢肺炎）確診病例。俄羅斯先前才剛宣布，將關閉遠東地區與中國的邊境，隨即爆發確診病例。<br />\n戈利科娃31日表示，這兩起病例分別出現在西伯利亞地區的外貝加爾邊疆區（Zabaykalsky Krai）和秋明州（Tyumen Oblast），2名患者均為中國公民。這是俄羅斯境內首次出現新型冠狀病毒確診個案。<br />\n俄羅斯外交部30日發表聲明，宣布關閉俄羅斯遠東地區與中國的邊界，並且暫停向中國公民簽發電子簽證。俄國外交部宣布，自2020年1月30日起，暫停為中國公民辦理用於經遠東地區、加里寧格勒邊境口岸及經聖彼得堡和列寧格勒州航空、海洋、汽車或人行口岸入境的電子簽證。<br />\n<br />\n此次出現確診病例的外貝加爾邊疆區與中國內蒙古接壤，而秋明州則未和中國邊境接壤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab4043b616a8bbca4ae876a2f6763fe4a84cc48","tid":1854440,"uid":308163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:12:30.000Z","msg":"厲害了 鄰國"},{"pid":"3d4df91447c29f002081333df6183bca0afc17bd","tid":1854440,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:18:37.000Z","msg":"得罪契哥?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cbd797a2b179f5f1d45464007863beccdd2400","tid":1854440,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"凍到俄羅斯 熱到泰國<br />\n隻病毒都生存到，仲要識彈出彈入高傳染性<br />\n有排爆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}